  _     _
 | |__ | |   browserlane
 | '_ \| |   browser automation for humans and AI agents
 | |_) | |   one binary · CLI + MCP · over WebDriver BiDi
 |_.__/|_|   v0.1.2

  Get started
    bl install                  download Chrome for Testing (run once)
    bl go https://example.com   open a URL
    bl screenshot -o page.png   capture the current page
    bl find role button         find elements semantically
    bl add-mcp claude           connect the MCP server to your agent

  Run bl --help to see every command, or bl <command> --help for details.
